TC01 – Positive Test Case
Title: Validate user registration with valid data

Pre-condition: User is on the registration page

Steps:

Enter valid username

Enter valid email address

Enter valid password

Click "Register"

Expected Result: Account created successfully, user redirected to homepage

Actual Result: Account created and redirected correctly

Status: Pass

TC02 – Positive Test Case
Title: Validate entering a valid promotion code

Pre-condition: User signed up and reached promotion code entry page

Steps:

Enter valid code (PROMO10)

Click "Apply"

Expected Result: System accepts code and applies 10% discount

Actual Result: Discount applied successfully

Status: Pass

TC03 – Negative Test Case
Title: Validate entering an invalid promotion code

Pre-condition: User signed up and wants to enter promotion code

Steps:

Enter invalid code (hh+78)

Click "Apply"

Expected Result: System rejects code and displays error message "Enter valid code"

Actual Result: Error message displayed correctly

Status: Pass

TC04 – Negative Test Case
Title: Guest user attempts to post an ad

Pre-condition: User is not logged in (guest mode)

Steps:

Open website as guest

Click "Post Ad"

Enter ad details and try to publish

Expected Result: System prevents action and requests login

Actual Result: Alert displayed "Please log in first"

Status: Pass
